Welcome to Level Up!

Here is how the half-day will go:

  • 1:00 - 1:10 pm: Join us for the all-team opening session. Here we will give you a warm welcome and provide a detailed information on how to navigate Level Up.
  • 1:10 - 1:20 pm: Transition
  • 1:20 - 2:30 pm: Unconference sessions — staff-led discussions in groups of 10 - 15; topics will cover working productively in government, managing people well, and boosting technical/agile skills
  • 2:30 - 2:40 pm: Transition
  • 2:40 - 3:40 pm: Snack party with assigned “tables” where you’ll have a chance to meet team members from around TTS. Bring a snack to enjoy!
  • 3:40 - 3:45 pm: Transition
  • 3:45 - 4:45 pm:Lessons learned sessions — staff-led discussions in groups of 10 - 15; these are stories of failure or wild success that others can learn from
  • 4:45 - 5:00 pm: All-team closing session. Now its time to say goodbye. Shout out what you learned (on slack) and hear about next steps.
